100%; vertical-align: middle; border: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;&quot; src=&quot;https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/-gnghANZaMmY/U_rlX5vXCrI/AAAAAAAAA8g/DqxyVJMuVig/w600-h502-no/cong-cu-seobrowser.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;SEO-browser&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;em&gt;C&amp;ocirc;ng cụ SEO-Browser&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #424242; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;C&amp;ocirc;ng cụ n&amp;agrave;y l&amp;agrave; rất tốt cho những người kh&amp;ocirc;ng muốn đi qua c&amp;aacute;c chi tiết kỹ thuật của c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng cụ t&amp;igrave;m kiếm khả năng tiếp cận. C&amp;ocirc;ng cụ n&amp;agrave;y cung cấp th&amp;ocirc;ng tin về:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 15px; color: #424242; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;li style=&quot;outline: 0px; list-style: inherit; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Dữ liệu thẻ meta&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li style=&quot;outline: 0px; list-style: inherit; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Robot.txt&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li style=&quot;outline: 0px; list-style: inherit; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Yếu tố Javascrip&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li style=&quot;outline: 0px; list-style: inherit; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Internal and external links&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li style=&quot;outline: 0px; list-style: inherit; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Tỷ lệ text ratio tr&amp;ecirc;n trang&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;h3 style=&quot;margin: 10px 0px; font-family: Arial; line-height: 40px; color: #424242; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 24.5px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Kỹ thuật&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #424242; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;9. Google Webmaster tools&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Đăng k&amp;yacute; trang web của bạn với Google Webmaster Tools cho c&amp;aacute;c truy vấn